summary: I'm young and passionate. I have experience in graphical design, digital surface design, textile printing and I dabble in photography. Always keeping up with the current trends, related technological and design innovations. I've also spent a lot of time being a dresser in film productions. It has taught me to be extremely fast on my feet.
